{"description":"[p]The pirates operate from hidden bases which we must find and eliminate to restore the safety in our sector. These bases are relocated regularly and so far they have managed to keep their coordinates secret. However, we extracted data from a damaged pirate vessel that was left drifting after a recent attack. While it doesn't reveal the location of their base, it allowed us to come up with a plan to track it down.[p]It looks like the pirates are using a hijacked communications relay hidden in the protoplanetary disk of the Arberon system to organize their forces. The coordinates we uncovered from the data files could lead us to this relay, codenamed [s:h]Hermes[].[p]Your task is to [b]find this relay, hack its software systems and then use it to reveal the location of the pirate base[]. Your ship has been equipped with the necessary electronic warfare and jamming equipment. If you stay within 150 meters of the relay for a short while, we will be able to take it over while also preventing the pirates to send a distress signal. Then you will need to make sure the relay stays operational and under our control until we can determine the location of the hidden base. Once we have retrieved the information, you are free to leave the area.[p]Beware, this mission takes place in a thick nebula! You will experience [b]reduced maneuverability and speed[] due to drag, [b]decreased sensor and visual range[] and [b]longer missile lock times[]!","nextMission":"holdingOut.json","environment":"arberon","anticipationTheme":"anticipation2","combatTheme":"combat3","teams":[{"faction":"empire"},{"faction":"pirates"}],"events":[{"trigger":{},"actions":[{"type":"message","delay":500,"params":{"textID":"start1"}},{"type":"message","delay":500,"params":{"textID":"start2"}}]},{"trigger":{"conditions":[{"type":"distance","subjects":{"squads":["marauder"]},"params":{"target":"alpha 1","maxDistance":3300,"which":"any"}}],"once":true},"actions":[{"type":"message","params":{"textI